1
01:19:13,873 --> 01:19:17,001
I am Arwen - I've come to help you.

2
01:19:19,420 --> 01:19:21,256
Hear my voice...

3
01:19:21,506 --> 01:19:23,633
Come back to the light.

4
01:19:55,164 --> 01:19:57,583
Stay with the Hobbits -
I'll send horses for you.

5
01:19:57,792 --> 01:19:59,460
I'm the faster rider - I'll take him

6
01:20:00,295 --> 01:20:01,671
The Road is too dangerous.

7
01:20:03,339 --> 01:20:05,383
If I can get across the river...

8
01:20:05,591 --> 01:20:08,177
...the power of my people
will protect him.

9
01:35:46,490 --> 01:35:48,867
The Shadow does not hold sway yet.

10
01:35:49,868 --> 01:35:53,497
Not over you... not over me.

11
01:36:04,841 --> 01:36:08,053
Do you remember when we first met?

12
01:36:11,598 --> 01:36:16,144
I thought I had strayed into a dream.

13
01:36:16,687 --> 01:36:19,189
Long years have passed.

14
01:36:20,899 --> 01:36:24,278
You did not have the cares you carry now.

15
01:36:25,737 --> 01:36:27,781
Do you remember what I told you?

16
01:40:44,955 --> 01:40:46,414
Sit down, Legolas.

17
01:46:13,142 --> 01:46:15,686
She wanted to protect her child...

18
01:46:17,521 --> 01:46:21,317
she thought in Rivendell
you would be safe.

19
02:31:14,382 --> 02:31:16,384
Welcome Legolas, son of Thranduil.

20
02:31:17,302 --> 02:31:19,971
Our Fellowship stands in your debt.

21
02:31:22,766 --> 02:31:24,476
Aragorn of the Dunedain...

22
02:31:25,101 --> 02:31:26,519
you are known to us.

23
02:48:55,109 --> 02:48:57,695
You are being tracked.

24
02:50:49,640 --> 02:50:50,682
For her love,

25
02:50:51,975 --> 02:50:57,314
I fear the grace of Arwen Evenstar
will diminish.

26
02:50:58,106 --> 02:51:01,401
I would have her leave these shores,

27
02:51:02,945 --> 02:51:05,864
and be with her people.

28
02:51:07,866 --> 02:51:13,580
I would have her take the ship to Valinor.

29
02:51:38,480 --> 02:51:39,773
Farewell.

30
02:51:43,652 --> 02:51:47,030
There is much you have yet to do.

31
02:51:53,537 --> 02:51:54,788
We shall not meet again...

32
02:51:54,997 --> 02:51:56,373
Elessar.

33
03:48:05,989 --> 03:48:07,991
[English]

